{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6326fafafc","title":"攻击肃反运动","origin":"《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"543e44c4ef","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"6326fafafc"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1008bd7208","name":"秦西灿"},{"id":"367e853735","name":"山东师范学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bb330a461a","type":"title","text":"攻击肃反运动","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6326fafafc"},{"id":"6cfe2293f2","type":"authors","text":"山东师范学院秦西灿","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6326fafafc"},{"id":"70842a89bb","type":"paragraph","text":"“肃反的错误，不仅发生在我们学校和山东，而全国也有，这是否党中央在贯彻肃反政策上有错误？如果这样，那末本院党委有说不出的苦衷。再说，有错必纠，如果党中央有指示，党委不贯彻，那末本院党委应负责，如果不知道，那么党中央也可能犯了官僚主义。我看党中央有宁左勿右的情况，有人说不要光责备春香，也不要光责备小姐，老夫人也应该负责任，我看这是对的。”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6326fafafc"}],"page":{"id":"b76135d1ad","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6326fafafc","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}